OL,3,CHull funeral inquiry: MP 'pushing' for
OL,4,Cindustry regulation
OL,6,FAn MP said it is a "glaring omission"
OL,7,Fnot to regulate funeral directors, as
OL,8,Fthe investigation into Legacy
OL,9,FIndependent Funeral Directors
OL,10,Fcontinues.
OL,12,FEarlier this month police received
OL,13,Freports of concerns for "care for the
OL,14,Fdeceased" at the -based funeral
OL,15,Fdirectors.
OL,17,FThirty-five bodies were removed from a
OL,18,Fbranch on Hessle Road and have now
OL,19,Fbeen identified.
