OL,3,CHull funeral inquiry: MP 'pushing' for
OL,4,Cindustry regulation
OL,6,FEmma Hardy, the MP for Hull West and
OL,7,FHessle says she is meeting government
OL,8,Fministers weekly as police inquiries
OL,9,Fcontinue.
OL,11,FA 46-year-old man and a 23-year-old
OL,12,Fwoman, who were arrested on suspicion
OL,13,Fof prevention of a lawful and decent
OL,14,Fburial, fraud by false representation
OL,15,Fand fraud by abuse of position, remain
OL,16,Fon bail.JMs Hardy revealed that
OL,17,FHumberside Police has a 100-strong
OL,18,Fteam working on the investigation in
OL,19,Fits major incident room.
