OL,3,CHull funeral inquiry: MP 'pushing' for
OL,4,Cindustry regulation
OL,6,F"It is a huge investigation and the
OL,7,Fpolice are working tirelessly on
OL,8,Fbehalf of the families who have been
OL,9,Faffected by this.J"I am in regular
OL,10,Fcontact with the Chief Constable and
OL,11,Fhis team and my job as MP for Hull
OL,12,FWest and Hessle is to push for
OL,13,Fregulation of the sector to try and
OL,14,Fensure that something like this can
OL,15,Fnever happen again.
OL,26,@qD@SOU
