OL,3,CHull funeral inquiry: MP 'pushing' for
OL,4,Cindustry regulation
OL,6,F"To that end I have been meeting with
OL,7,Fministers every week since this matter
OL,8,Femerged. The government has promised
OL,9,Fthere will be a call for evidence
OL,10,Fimminently.J"Having spoken to experts
OL,11,Fwithin the sector it's clear that
OL,12,Fmortuaries and crematoriums are
OL,13,Fregulated but for some reason funeral
OL,14,Fdirectors are not. That's a glaring
OL,15,Fomission which needs to be dealt with."
OL,17,FOn Saturday, 23 March, a congregation
OL,18,Fof around a hundred people, including
OL,19,Fsome families whose loved ones'
OL,20,Ffunerals have been handled by Legacy,
OL,21,Fattended a vigil at Hull Minster.
