OL,6,FAmong them was Billie-Jo Suffill, a
OL,7,Fmother of three who used the company
OL,8,Ffor the cremation of her brother and
OL,9,Ffather who died in 2022.
OL,11,FShe said the service was
OL,12,F"heartbreaking but nice at the same
OL,13,Ftime."
OL,15,FShe said: "I was ringing all the
OL,16,Ffuneral directors and no one would
OL,17,Fhelp me and then Legacy did so he was
OL,18,Flike my hero. He took my dad and
OL,19,Fbrother off me and I was proud of
OL,20,Fmyself thinking I have done them proud.
