OL,6,F"I never received my dad's ashes and
OL,7,Fnow I have a fear that Dwain's might
OL,8,Fnot even be his. So whether it turns
OL,9,Fout alright the trauma is still real."
OL,11,FThe Bishop of Hull, Rt Rev Dr Eleanor
OL,12,FSanderson said: "What I think is so
OL,13,Fdifficult about this is the
OL,14,Fdishonourable journey that some people
OL,15,Fmay have had, and so tonight we want
OL,16,Fto honour and dignify all the families
OL,17,Fas well as their loved ones."
